verbose_text: NTRC overexpression enhances reduction in the PQ pool in darkness, increases the magnitude of pmf and PSI yield in comparison with WT in low light and upon increases in light intensity, and enhances the acidification of the lumen under all light intensities in an NDH dependent manner [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: NTRC overexpression enhances reduction in the PQ pool in darkness, increases the magnitude of pmf and PSI
